OL,3,C'It takes 15 minutes': People in Wales
OL,4,Curged to learn lifesaving skills of CPR
OL,6,FTwo young people from South Wales who
OL,7,Fwere born with heart conditions are
OL,8,Furging people to learn how to do CPR,
OL,9,Fas new figures released by British
OL,10,FHeart Foundation state around 800,000
OL,11,Fin Wales are yet to learn the skills
OL,12,Fto save a life.
OL,14,F17-year-old Lily from Carmarthenshire
OL,15,Fand 18-year-old Garyn from Neath were
OL,16,Fboth born with Tetralogy of Fallot, a
OL,17,Fbirth defect that affects normal blood
OL,18,Fflow through the heart.
