OL,3,C'It takes 15 minutes': People in Wales
OL,4,Curged to learn lifesaving skills of CPR
OL,6,FGaryn said: "It's a subject that
OL,7,Fdefinitely needs to be talked about.
OL,8,FFor my condition, I've been quite
OL,9,Funlucky in some retrospect but then
OL,10,Fquite lucky for having amazing doctors.
OL,12,F"I think (CPR) is an important skill
OL,13,Fto know, it's not very often you're
OL,14,Fgoing to have to use it, but if you do
OL,15,Fknow it, you could save someone's life
OL,16,Fin the future."
