OL,3,C'It takes 15 minutes': People in Wales
OL,4,Curged to learn lifesaving skills of CPR
OL,6,FA survey conducted for the BHF by
OL,7,FCensuswide, found that 16-26 year olds
OL,8,Fin Wales are the most confident
OL,9,Fgeneration in performing CPR, with 68%
OL,10,Fof respondents trained. On the other
OL,11,Fhand only 46% of people aged 59 to 77
OL,12,Fsaid they were comfortable in their
OL,13,Fability to save a life.
OL,15,FLily said: "I learnt CPR in school,
OL,16,Fit's such a valuable skill to know
OL,17,Fbecause as a young person, I think you
OL,18,Fshould know it. To anyone thinking of
OL,19,Flearning the skill, I'd definitely go
OL,20,Ffor it, it only takes 15 minutes to
OL,21,Flearn."
