OL,3,C'It takes 15 minutes': People in Wales
OL,4,Curged to learn lifesaving skills of CPR
OL,6,FOnly one in 20 people survive an out-
OL,7,Fof-hospital cardiac arrest in Wales, a
OL,8,Fstatistic the BHF Cymru is determined
OL,9,Fto improve.
OL,11,FAdam Fletcher, Head of BHF Cymru
OL,12,Fadded: "Without CPR, the chances of
OL,13,Fsomeone surviving a cardiac arrest are
OL,14,Fvery very low. We've made it as easy
OL,15,Fas possible for everyone to learn CPR,
OL,16,Fyou can go online and on your mobile."
